The '''F-s3.2 flight avionics system''' was the primary flight control system for both the [[TIE/ln space superiority starfighter/Legends|TIE/LN starfighter]] and the [[TIE/sa tactical bomber/Legends|TIE/sa bomber]]. The system was developed and manufactured by [[Sienar Fleet Systems/Legends|Sienar Fleet Systems]], who also built the [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] themselves.

